Wattpad Story Scraper:

This is some python code that will take a link to a Wattpad story (regardless of the chapter) 
and copy the entirety of the story into text files.
-----------------------------
Way to use:
input:
python watScrp.py [url to wattpad story]

output:
[list links to all of the chapters]
Chapter_0 writing
Chapter_1 writing
...

input:
dir

output:
Chapter_0.txt
Chapter_1.txt
...

-----------------------------

If no argument is given, the scraper will automatically scrape the wattpad story "the shy girl's got a gun"

-----------------------------

link to "the shy girl's got a gun":
https://www.wattpad.com/1069480-the-shy-girl-has-a-gun
